.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, indie, house, country
1. the fan house is between the fan country and the fan indie##2
2. the fan soul is on the left of the fan indie##1
3. the fan soul is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2    |   3   |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | indie | house | country |

