.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, november, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in november##2
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |    2     |   3    |     4     |
| Birthday   | april | july | february | november |

